.Dd January 16, 1999
.Dt YP 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm nis ,
.Nm yp
.Nd description of the NIS (formerly YP) subsystem
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm ypbind
.Op Fl ypset
.Nm ypbind
.Op Fl ypsetme
.Pp
